Package cggGCode

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    compensacionContorno
    This class implements the necessary algorithms to calculate a new contour compensating the radius of the selected tool to operate.
    GCode
    This class implements the necessary algorithms to translate all the collected data into G-Code
    GCodeMetodoContorneado
    This class implements the necessary algorithms to generate the G-Code from contours.
    GCodeMetodoGeneral
    This class implements the necessary algorithms to generate the G-Code from any list of entities.
    GCodeMetodoTaladrado
    This class implements the necessary algorithms to generate the G-Code from a list of holes.
    SelectorDeDirectorio
    This class implements a directory chooser to save files
